# GitHub Actions Configuration

## Automated Code Review
The project includes a sophisticated GitHub Actions workflow at [.github/workflows/code-reviewer.yaml](mdc:.github/workflows/code-reviewer.yaml) that:

- Triggers on PR events (opened, synchronize, reopened, ready_for_review)
- Uses Cursor CLI for automated code review
- Requires `CURSOR_API_KEY` environment secret
- Provides inline comments with emoji categorization

